messages.text: Update. Travis is now at the bar with Christa.
I suggest you go there to confront him
I’m out of town all this week
Science lab retreat in NY for my thesis. I thought you knew that
You being gone explains his philandering. He also met an older woman
Did you get a photo of them?
Only him but not the woman. It looked like they were involved though
Could have been his mom, but not dressed that way.
Skinny jeans, trying to look younger.
I’d forward if I had any
I need proof Travis having sex with this Christa. Get me that!
Roger. I mean 10-4. Yes. They’ve finished their wine
Get those photos and let’s put this case to bed
What’s our plan once this case is closed?
You bill me for the hours
We’ll see. Let me know when they’re in Christa’s apartment
Got it. Sending one of the photos now
There’s a bunch. This guy’s libido is impressive. He must be taking something
Email me all the photos and I’ll forward them to my client
Don’t let anyone see you getting your camera
I’ve got my bucket and squeegee. Don’t worry
Elise, I’ve emailed requested photos. Check your inbox.
A few emails due to file size
That’s him alright. How could he?
I’ll call off the wedding. I trust you can be discreet?
My professional reputation relies on discretion
Thank you. Please send me the bill beyond your retainer
I’m sorry it turned out this way
Thanks for everything. You were great.
Roger. Let me know how many hours you put in
This was fun, us working together. Like old times
You can’t force me to cash the check
What about the beers you bought?
I would have bought beers even if I wasn’t working. No biggie
Mike, you need to take a fee
A strange case, can’t put my finger on it.
In my dad’s day he would meet clients face to face.
I’d see them come in the office when I was helping out
Use his gut, but I never got a pulse on this client
You spoke to her on the phone, right?
All email and text. She’s paying through PayPal
So what’s so weird about it?
Something’s not right, I can feel it
It does to me. Let me get back to you
Looking at wedding registry now. My suspicions were correct
She’s the blonde you photographed with Travis at the library
The mother is named Elise. She’s the one that hired me
So the mother of the bride hired you to prove her future son in law was cheating?
A photo of Janice and Travis is on the bridal registry.
Elise is the bride’s mother from the engagement announcement.
I confirmed with the wedding coordinator.
Because private eyes root out the truth. Dad taught me that
Not for me. Finding the truth is what private eyes do
Click below to see what happens next...
